caption.text:
Hello, my name is Joel and I want to tell the world that I stand #WithRefugees.
.
Do you know that there are more than 14,000 asylum seekers and refugees in Indonesia? Do you know that Indonesia is not a signatory to the UN's 1951 Convention on Refugees and its 1967 Protocol? Therefore, Indonesia is not obliged to take in refugees or provide assistance to refugees.
.
But, on December 31, 2016, The Government of Indonesia has passed Presidential Decree 125/2016 regarding Refugees from Abroad. This regulation fills a legal vacuum which has long affected asylum seekers and refugees in Indonesia.
.
Following the act of the government, I believe that protecting refugees is not somebody else's problem. All of us can help make refugees thrive.
.
I support FPCI UI Refugee Care event to visit Cisarua Refugee Learning Center because i believe that a first contact initiative is important to better know and befriend them that are here, so i just have to come :)
.
#RefugeeCare
#TogethertoShare
#FPCIUI
#TogethertoGather
